Nairavin.com is here to guide many car buyers. You may not need to buy any car as from this moment again without understanding the genesis of the vehicle you are buying, It’s like building a house on a sinking sand. Getting money to buy car may be difficult for everyone in Nigeria because our government do not have plan for us when it comes to getting loan to be able to take care of some basic needs. In USA getting car is easier as far as you have a good credit report which will qualify you for getting a brand new car irrespective of the job you are doing but here in Nigeria buying a car is as difficult as getting a gold for a middle class not to talk of the poor masses. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-839586 size-large" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/PHOTO-2020-08-08-18-24-46-1024x567.jpg.webp" alt="" width="740" height="410" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/PHOTO-2020-08-08-18-24-46-1024x567.jpg.webp 1024w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/PHOTO-2020-08-08-18-24-46-300x166.jpg.webp 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/PHOTO-2020-08-08-18-24-46.jpg.webp 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px"> While you save money to buy car, it is important for you to understand the kind of car you are buying, It is sad that car dealer will never tell you the secret of the car you are buying because the outer of the car is beautiful while the engine and other features are bad which is like pouring water into an open basket. Many car dealers in Nigeria will decide to buy car with exceeded limit mileage, A car that has gone a very long distance.why?The more the mileage the riskier the engine will be. Nigerian should take note of that.
We are imploring every Nigerian never to buy any car without asking for the (Vehicle Identification number or CHASIS NUMBER). Example 5TDYK3DC8D5290235 Which is usually called CHASIS Number and usually located at the dashboard of the windshield or you can check that inside your custom paper or you can ask your mechanic to help you find it. Below are the benefits of the (VEHICLE IDENTIFICATION or CHASIS NUMBER). 1. Allow you to know if the mileage has been compromised. 2. Allow you to know whether the Airbag has deflated or not. 3. It helps you to know the number of past users. 4. It helps to detect whether the Engine has been changed or not 5. It also allows you to know the exact color as at the time of buying. 6. It helps you distinguish between the clean, salvage or flood title.  Benefit of using our company 1. We quickly send you a comprehensive report before you buy that car. 2. We look out for you to make sure you don’t buy packaging car. 3. Using our report to buy any car will give you rest of mind. 4. We serve as your guardian in making a decision on any car. BETTER TO SPEND LESS TO GET A REPORT THAN TO SPEND BIG AND GET BAD CAR. Feel free to chat us 08093185000
